All Classes

Class Summary
Class Description
FileHandler
The FileHandler is responsible for saving and loading task lists to and from file.
Parser
The Parser is responsible for getting user input.
Printer
The Responder is responsible for printing information to the terminal.
Task
Models a task with a task title, due date, done status and project.
TaskComparator
Defines comparators for the Task class by due date or project.
TaskList
Models a collection of tasks that can be sorted by date and project.
TaskTest
Tests for the Task class that models a task with a task title, due date, status and project.
ToDoListApp
This class implements a to do list application.
Validator
The Validator checks that the input is valid.
